          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For portions of the 259.4 MeV run and the entire",
                "254.6 MeV run, a 55 mug/cm**2 thick carbon stripper",
                "foil was mounted directly upstream of the target to",
                "increase the charge state of the beam.",
                "For the 231.2 MeV irradiation, targets with average",
                "thicknesses of 558-mug/cm**2 206PbS, 522-mug/cm**2",
                " 207PbS and 531-mug/cm**2 208PbS were used. All PbS",
                "targets were covered with 10-mug/cm**2 C-nat.",
                "244PuO(2) targets (isotopic composition- 97.9% 244Pu,",
                " 1.3% 242Pu, 0.7% 240Pu, and less than 0.1% other were",
                "used. irradiated.  The 244PuO(2) targets were prepared",
                "on 2.22+-0.05 mum thick Ti foils by electrochemical",
                "deposition from isobutanolic solution. Over the course",
                "of the experiment, four 244Pu target segments with a",
                "beam dose weighted average target thickness of",
                " 438-mug/cm**2 244Pu as 495-mug/cm**2  244PuO(2) were",
                "irradiated with typical beam intensities of 2*e+12",
                "particles 1/s."
              ]
            }
          ],
